Packaging hints
===============

This file contains useful info for (re)building the packaging of the
source.

Packaged using GIT
------------------

This packaging is maintained with the use of GIT.

Upstream source is in the "upstream" branch, and Debian-related
packaging in "master".

The following commands can be used to fetch and build the package:

aptitude install git-buildpackage
git clone git://git.debian.org/git/collab-maint/sugar-base
cd sugar-base
git fetch origin upstream:upstream
git-buildpackage

